N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 83-2.16 - Certificate of need and other requirements

State Regulations

Nothing in this Subpart shall relieve parties from any responsibility for compliance with laws or regulations governing certificate of need or other approval or notice submission requirements. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10
§§
83-2.16

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
